4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program lasts 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week with a maximum of 18 students per class. Participants will gain expertise in Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. The curriculum supports both English and Spanish, and upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The median salary for cybersecurity professionals in the U.S. is $103,560. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop